## Layout Route Patterns

### Layout Route Structure
```tsx
// Route configuration
layout("routes/resource/Layout.tsx", [
  route("/welcome", "routes/welcome.tsx"),
  route("/org/settings", "routes/org/settings.tsx"),
  // Nested routes inherit layout
])
```

### Layout Component Pattern
```tsx
export default function Layout({ loaderData }: Route.ComponentProps) {
  return (
    <div className="layout-container">
      <Header {...loaderData.headerProps} />
      <div className="content-wrapper">
        <Navigation />
        <main>
          <Outlet />
        </main>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```

## Best Practices

### Performance
- Use `contain-layout` for layout containment
- Implement proper overflow handling
- Minimize layout shifts with fixed dimensions

### Accessibility
- Maintain proper heading hierarchy
- Ensure keyboard navigation works
- Use semantic HTML structure

### Maintainability
- Keep layout logic separate from content
- Use consistent spacing utilities
- Document responsive breakpoints

### Dark Mode
- Always provide dark mode variants
- Use CSS custom properties for theme switching
- Test all layouts in both themes
